  "cataloging_subject": {
    "id": "work:CME00081",
    "unit_type": "edited_selection",
    "label": "Short Pieces from MS. Cotton Galba E. IX",
    "scope_note": "The cataloged subject is Joseph Hall's exact 1895 edited selection from British Library Cotton MS Galba E IX, ff. 3-114, not the complete manuscript and not one medieval authorial work. Hall numbered three units, but modern DIMEV records show that his third unit joins two distinct Middle English poems under separate Latin verse frames. The selection therefore contains four anonymous medieval poems in three Hall-numbered divisions."
  },
